#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:1
msgid "PyRepl 代码执行"
msgstr "PyRepl Code Execution"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:3
msgid ""
"SimpleLLMFunc 提供内置的 PyRepl 支持，允许 LLM 在一个连续上下文中执行 Python "
"代码。与传统的一次性代码执行不同，PyRepl 保持变量和状态，让 LLM 可以分步执行复杂任务。"
msgstr ""
"SimpleLLMFunc includes built-in PyRepl support, allowing LLMs to execute "
"Python code in a continuous context. Unlike one-shot code execution, "
"PyRepl preserves variables and state so the LLM can solve complex tasks "
"step by step."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:5
msgid "功能特性"
msgstr "Features"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:7
msgid "**轻量实现**：仅依赖 Python 内置模块，无需 jupyter_client"
msgstr ""
"**Lightweight implementation**: Depends only on Python built-ins; no "
"`jupyter_client` required"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:8
msgid "**连续上下文**：变量在多次调用间持久化，LLM 可以分步执行任务"
msgstr ""
"**Continuous context**: Variables persist across calls, enabling step-by-"
"step execution"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:9
msgid "**实时 Streaming**：通过 `event_emitter` 实时获取 stdout/stderr 输出"
msgstr ""
"**Real-time streaming**: Receive stdout/stderr in real time via "
"`event_emitter`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:10
msgid "**异步不阻塞**：代码执行在独立线程运行，不阻塞主事件循环（适合 TUI/流式 UI）"
msgstr ""
"**Async and non-blocking**: Code runs in a dedicated thread and does not "
"block the main event loop (suitable for TUI/streaming UIs)"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:11
msgid "**Session 隔离**：不同的 PyRepl 实例相互独立，互不影响"
msgstr ""
"**Session isolation**: Different PyRepl instances are independent and do "
"not interfere"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:12
msgid "**完整工具集**：提供 execute_code、reset_repl、list_variables 等工具"
msgstr ""
"**Complete toolset**: Provides `execute_code`, `reset_repl`, "
"`list_variables`, and more"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:13
msgid ""
"**超时保护**：单次 `execute_code` 默认 120 秒活动执行超时；等待 `input()` "
"不计时，且每次收到输入后会重置超时窗口；单次 `input()` 默认 300 秒空闲超时"
msgstr ""
"**Timeout protection**: `execute_code` has a default 120-second active "
"execution timeout; waiting on `input()` does not consume it, and each "
"accepted input resets the timeout window; each `input()` also has a "
"default 300-second idle timeout"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:15
msgid "快速开始"
msgstr "Quick Start"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:17
msgid "基本用法"
msgstr "Basic Usage"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:49
msgid "多 PyRepl 隔离"
msgstr "Multiple PyRepl Isolation"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:66
msgid "工具详解"
msgstr "Tool Details"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:68
msgid "execute_code"
msgstr "execute_code"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:70
msgid "执行 Python 代码，返回执行结果。"
msgstr "Execute Python code and return the execution result."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:72
msgid ""
"说明：`execute_code` 默认有 120 秒活动执行超时保护。等待 `input()` 期间不会计入超时；每次 `input()` "
"成功回填后会重置超时计时。同时，单次 `input()` 默认 300 秒空闲超时。任一超时触发时 `success=False`，并在 "
"`error`/`stderr` 中返回超时信息。"
msgstr ""
"Note: `execute_code` has a default 120-second active execution timeout. "
"Waiting on `input()` does not count against this budget, and each "
"successful input submission resets the timeout window. In addition, each "
"`input()` has a default 300-second idle timeout. If either timeout is "
"triggered, `success=False`, and timeout details are returned in "
"`error`/`stderr`."

